_______________________________________________________________________________
"Crystalize"      
        A psionicist with this power can use the residual psychic
        energy left behind when the soul departs a corpse in order
        to create a crystal which stores psychic power (SP).  The
        quality of the crystal created depends on a random chance
        dependent on guild level.  No matter what the quality of
        the crystal resulting, the power costs 20 sp. To reclaim the
	power stored in the crystal, you simply 'drain crystal'.
 
SP Cost:  20            Guild Level:  6         Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  crystalize
